com.facebook.buck.json

Class HybridProjectBuildFileParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.json.HybridProjectBuildFileParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProjectBuildFileParser, AutoCloseable

    public class HybridProjectBuildFileParser
extends Object
implements ProjectBuildFileParser
    Hybrid project build file parser that uses Python DSL or Skylark depending on syntax requested for each individual build file.

    The default is Python DSL, but clients can explicitly request desired syntax by adding parser directive to the beginning of the build file followed by one of the supported HybridProjectBuildFileParser.Syntax values.
